dc_title_s: A correct map of the Pacific Northwest showing rail & steamer lines of the O. R. & N. Co.; Title on map: Map of the Oregon Railroad and Navigation Co.
dc_description_s: Cover title. Copyright, 1898, by Poole Bros., Chicago. 1 map: col.; 59 x 55 cm, folded in cover 16 x 11 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
